  <description type="morphology">Leaves: petioles 1–7(–12+) cm; blades 6–12(–20+) × 5–12(–18+) cm. Peduncles 1–6(–12+) mm. Involucres 2–3 mm. Phyllaries: outer 5 ± herbaceous, sericeous to strigillose, inner scarious to membranous, glabrous or glabrate. Paleae 2–2.5 mm. Pistillate florets: corollas 0.1–0.5 mm, or 0. Functionally staminate florets: corollas 2–2.5 mm. Cypselae 2–2.5(–3) mm. 2n = 36.</description>
